========================
AWS 17 NEW FEATURES LIST
========================

Copyright (C) 2015, AdaCore

This file contains a list of new features introduced in AWS.
A full description of all AWS features can be found in the AWS
documentation.

An ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD) appears in parentheses after the
description line. This date shows the implementation date
of the feature.

New features in AWS 17
----------------------

NF-17-OA13-048 Server Name Identification (SNI) support (2015-11-17)

    Server can provide different certificates for the clients asking for
    different host names on the same physical IP address.

NF-17-OA28-005 Add support for non-blocking WebSockets (2015-11-17)

    When sending a message to a set of recipient (URI broadcast) the
    sending is not blocking. The fastest sockets will get served first
    and won't be blocked by slower ones.
